{"tid":1685960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"克什米爾直轄區分治「中国領土」印度稱內政北京無權評論","createTime":"2019-11-01T00:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T06:05:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":68,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"ed96bdab382f858c1749786aa13382f2249ebfbd","tid":1685960,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:43:59.000Z","msg":"印度今天成立查摩與克什米爾中央直轄行政區及拉達克中央直轄區，中國外交部稱此舉是非法而無效的，印度外交部稍後聲明表示，這是印度內政，中國無權發表評論。<br />\n<br />\n印度外交部發言人庫瑪（Raveesh Kumar）在一份聲明中表示，中國深知印度在此一問題的一貫和明確立場，把過去的查摩與克什米爾省（Jammu and Kashmir）分為查摩與克什米爾中央直轄行政區及拉達克中央直轄行政區，完全是印度的內政。<br />\n<br />\n庫瑪說，印度不希望中國等國對印度內部事務發表評論，就像印度拒絕評論他國內部事務一樣。<br />\n<br />\n他說，「中國繼續在查摩與克什米爾中央直轄區及拉達克中央直轄區占領大片土地」，根據所謂的1963年中國與巴基斯坦邊界協定，還從巴基斯坦占領的克什米爾「非法奪取印度領土」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201910310401.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201910310401.aspx&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eH4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=145f9afd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201910310401.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"3169ab6c81bb637858451c7998e3b5d8bfba494f","tid":1685960,"uid":261433,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求共產黨心理陰影面積"},{"pid":"8536db2dc256ebd8fc0c61deeb842eee471a52db","tid":1685960,"uid":301915,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"ed96bdab382f858c1749786aa13382f2249ebfbd","tid":1685960,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:43:59.000Z","msg":"印度今天成立查摩與克什米爾中央直轄行政區及拉達克中央直轄區，中國外交部稱此舉是非法而無效的，印度外交部稍後聲明表示，這是印度內政，中國無權發表評論。<br />\n<br />\n印度外交部發言人庫瑪（Raveesh Kumar）在一份聲明中表示，中國深知印度在此一問題的一貫和明確立場，把過去的查摩與克什米爾省（Jammu and Kashmir）分為查摩與克什米爾中央直轄行政區及拉達克中央直轄行政區，完全是印度的內政。<br />\n<br />\n庫瑪說，印度不希望中國等國對印度內部事務發表評論，就像印度拒絕評論他國內部事務一樣。<br />\n<br />\n他說，「中國繼續在查摩與克什米爾中央直轄區及拉達克中央直轄區占領大片土地」，根據所謂的1963年中國與巴基斯坦邊界協定，還從巴基斯坦占領的克什米爾「非法奪取印度領土」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201910310401.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201910310401.aspx&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eH4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=145f9afd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201910310401.aspx</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:47:02.000Z","msg":"粗暴干涉印度內政，分裂印度必粉身碎骨"},{"pid":"b59b277a2ece5426a9f0bf49d5ef29614d39bce4","tid":1685960,"uid":258649,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:48:35.000Z","msg":"阿爽會回番佢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d572dbd92b53208f26121875a923425f1f2063d7","tid":1685960,"uid":265881,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:49:16.000Z","msg":"以支矛攻支盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa0c483323ee158e2d1fc8d8e457bdc76f79437","tid":1685960,"uid":10890,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:52:02.000Z","msg":"以支之矛攻支之盾"},{"pid":"623dae7ade8ba87eb4e4320f175a3b6c79f04db5","tid":1685960,"uid":22624,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b59b277a2ece5426a9f0bf49d5ef29614d39bce4","tid":1685960,"uid":258649,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:48:35.000Z","msg":"阿爽會回番佢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:54:17.000Z","msg":"自古以來"},{"pid":"ead03a8e9d1374410f468805e9a01ad10fbe2feb","tid":1685960,"uid":111576,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:59:37.000Z","msg":"印度佬「不容許外部勢力對我國內政說三道四，一切試圖分裂本國國土完整的邪惡陰謀必會粉身碎骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」"},{"pid":"386e1a7